      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The program for the annual\ncounty teachers institute has been\ncompleted by County Superinten-\ndent Watkins. Sessions will open\nin the high school building Octo-\nDer % and continue until Oc-\ntober &c.\n\n\nThe list of special lecturers and\ninstructors this year covers a wide\nrange and includes some of the\nbest talent In the country. Edward\nS. Meany, of the state university;\nH. c. Sampson, Of the state college\nat Pullman, and representatives of\nthe state normals are listed for the\ninstitute.\n\n\next Monday morning the sessions\nwill open with Professor Sampson\naddress on The New Education."
    }
